---
name: conformance-content-binding
---

# Values

```yaml @id=binding-values
user:
  role: Engineer
  name: Ada
active: true
count: 42
empty: null
```

# Template

${user.name}|${user}|${active}|${count}|${empty}|${missing.path}|${bad-path}

| Kind | Value |
| :--- | ---: |
| Bool | ${active} |

## Child

child=${user.role}

# Runner

[contentData, contentSection, contentBind, contentPlainText](std/content.ssc)

```scalascript
val bindings = contentData("binding-values").get
val template = contentSection("template").get
println(contentPlainText(contentBind(template, bindings)))
```
